## Who we are

Our website address is: https://sunnypatel.co.uk.

## Comments

When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, including the visitor's IP address and browser user agent string for spam detection purposes.

An anonymized string created from your email address may be provided to the Gravatar service. The Gravatar service privacy policy is available at https://automattic.com/privacy/. After comment approval, your profile picture becomes visible publicly.

## Media

You should avoid uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS). Visitors can download and extract location data from images on the website.

## Cookies

Comments, login information, and screen display preferences are saved in cookies. Comment cookies last one year. Login cookies persist for two days, with "Remember Me" extending to two weeks. Screen options cookies last one year. Article editing cookies expire after one day.

## Embedded content from other websites

Articles may include embedded content. These external websites may collect your data, use cookies, and monitor your interactions.

## Who we share your data with

Password reset emails include your IP address.

## How long we retain your data

Comments and metadata are retained indefinitely for automatic approval of follow-up comments. Registered users' profile information can be viewed, edited, or deleted anytime by the user or website administrators.

## What rights you have over your data

You can request an exported file of your personal data or request erasure, except data required for administrative, legal, or security purposes.

## Where your data is sent

Visitor comments may be checked through automated spam detection services.
